  "title": "Production Operator | 5 Days (MNC) | Tuas",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a global MNC in life science sector.</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Tuas area</strong><br /><strong>Working Hour: 5-day, Rotating Shifts</strong><br /><strong>Salary: Basic + Allowances + AWS</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Production Operator:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle, weigh, and dispense bulk raw materials for dry powder production, ensuring accuracy and compliance with safety and quality standards.</li><li>Operate and assemble production equipment for powder transfer, blending, and milling according to established procedures.</li><li>Carry out cleaning and sanitisation of production areas and equipment in line with GMP, EHS, and contamination control requirements.</li><li>Ensure all processes follow SOPs, Good Documentation Practices (GDP), and workplace safety guidelines.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min ‘O’ level</li><li>Experience working in manufacturing environment</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
